OL,3,CCharities' anger as government
OL,4,C'downgrades' disabilities minister role
OL,6,FCharities have expressed their anger
OL,7,Fafter the government downgraded its
OL,8,Fdisability minister role during
OL,9,FDisability History Month.
OL,11,FThe position, left vacant when Tom
OL,12,FPursglove was made legal migration
OL,13,Fminister last week, will now be held
OL,14,Fby Mims Davies, who said she is
OL,15,F"honoured" to have been given the role.
OL,17,FHowever, she confirmed she will have a
OL,18,F"continued focus on social mobility",
OL,19,Fafter she was appointed minister for
OL,20,Fsocial mobility, youth and progression
OL,21,Flast year.
